# PollCraft - Polling App Rules

You are an AI assistant helping with a Next.js 14+ polling application called "PollCraft" that uses Supabase for backend services and real-time functionality.

## Project Architecture

### Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ with App Router
- **Database**: Supabase (PostgreSQL with real-time subscriptions)
- **Authentication**: Supabase Auth (email/password)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 + shadcn/ui components
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **State Management**: React hooks + custom hooks for real-time data
- **TypeScript**: Strict mode enabled with comprehensive database types

